Class SvgDots.Dot

  • java.lang.Object
    • sph.vaadin.ui.svg.SvgDots.Dot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable
    Enclosing class:
    SvgDots

    public static class SvgDots.Dot
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    Dot contains all the required information about a single SVG dot in SvgDots component.

    Note: Dot is a JavaBeans Component.
